## ЁЯУИ COMBO STRATEGY: Use Both Styles Smartly

| Content Type                    | Format     | Frequency    |
| ------------------------------- | ---------- | ------------ |
| **Short Motivation (30sтАУ1min)** | Faceless   | Daily Shorts |
| **Career Tips / Talk**          | Face-based | 3├Ч per week  |
| **Success Story / Documentary** | Faceless   | 1├Ч per week  |
| **Live Chat or Weekly Recap**   | Face-based | 1├Ч per week  |

This gives you:
тЬЕ Fast content flow (faceless)
тЬЕ Deep audience connection (face-based)
тЬЕ High CTR (motivational thumbnails + expressive face)

